description.ar:
لمحبي الدجاج!
هو مفهوم توصيل ساندويتش تشيك في دبي.
الدجاج ، باعتباره العنصر الأساسي في القائمة ، يقدم المفهوم مجموعة واسعة من السندويشات اللذيذة والمرضية حقًا ، وهو مثالي لتناول طعام الغداء أو العشاء ، بالطريقة الأكثر ملاءمة مع أفضل قيمة ممكنة مقابل المال!
description.en:
For the chick lovers!
is a Chick sandwich delivery concept in Dubai.
Chicken, being the core item on the menu, the concept offers a wide range of flavourful & truly satisfying sandwiches, perfect for lunch or dinner, in the most convenient way with the best value for money possible!
Fresh brioche bun, double beef patty, double cheese, lollo bionda, some diced red onion, little mustard, our special sauce, and smok'd brisket carnitas on top.
Fresh brioche bun, double beef patty, double cheese, dill pickles, smok'd bacon and fried onion ring on top, with little mustard and some of our homemade smok'd hickory sauce.
Fresh brioche bun, double beef patty, double cheese, some tomato, lollo bionda, a little red onion, mustard, sweet relish, crowned with smok'd Pastrami.
The famous one and only Mattar Farm brisket sandwich. Now better than ever! Smok'd brisket with mixed cabbage, carrot, little onion pickles, dill pickles and BBQ Creamy Sauce
Smok'd brisket, a mix of cheddar cheese in toasted fresh bread.
Hand breaded chicken, lollo bionda lettuce, tomatoes, some dill pickles, unsweetened coleslaw, some sriracha mayo in a toasted fresh brioche bun.
Freshly smoked Pastrami, a little mustard and dill pickle.
A generous portion of freshly smok'd pastrami, lollo bionda, tomatoes, with a little house mustard and some chipotle mayo.
